623
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:17,840
Who exactly is she?

624
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,869
I think she simply wants to repudiate the bill!

625
00:34:19,870 --> 00:34:20,869
No, no.

626
00:34:20,870 --> 00:34:22,429
I didn't mean that!

627
00:34:22,430 --> 00:34:24,980
When I woke up this morning, I found my purse missing.

628
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:26,559
I was in a hurry for the exam.

629
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:28,910
Then I left the pendant as a pledge

630
00:34:28,910 --> 00:34:30,469
