635
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:40,050
Who are you trying to fool?

636
00:34:40,050 --> 00:34:42,150
It's not a useless stone!

637
00:34:42,150 --> 00:34:44,709
- You're obviously trying to repudiate the bill!
- I'm not!

638
00:34:44,709 --> 00:34:46,840
